snippet.title: Announcing The Demo of Business Heroes: Street Grub
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1429080/
Wishlist Now!

Inspired by Lemonade Tycoon (loved by millions), this turn-based strategy game lets you create delicious recipes and set the best prices to attract customers. Order the right amount of ingredients for tomorrow’s burgers and research ways to grow and improve to solve tricky problems!
